# Generic mapping file for outrun games
# Author: RedOne87

#Notice: Gas and Break calibration is peculiar for you are only allowed to calibrate it within the range ~[0x10:0xE0] instead of [0x00:0xFF].
#		 Otherwise the game will give you an error. So you have to start calibration having your analog input outside this forbidden "deadzone" area.

# Include the generic mapping file for driving games
INCLUDE generic-driving

# Change View: P1 down
CONTROLLER_BUTTON_B CONTROLLER_1 BUTTON_DOWN PLAYER_1
# Booster: P2 Down 
CONTROLLER_BUTTON_A CONTROLLER_1 BUTTON_DOWN PLAYER_2
